25:23.000 --> 25:26.000
The second force is players from other industries,

25:26.000 --> 25:33.000
which are able to influence the situation in the industry in which we work with our competitors.

25:33.000 --> 25:40.000
The third force is clients, with whom we trade in terms of price and payment conditions,

25:40.000 --> 25:45.000
